lead_paragraph: Arsenal manager Arsene Wenger has confirmed that midfielder Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain has been sidelined for weeks after suffering a knee injury in Tuesday night's 2-0 Champions League last-16, first leg defeat by Barcelona.

headline.print_headline: Oxlade-Chamberlain Out for Weeks With Knee Injury, Says Wenger
headline.main: Oxlade-Chamberlain Out for Weeks With Knee Injury, Says Wenger
